ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 20th day of May, 2015, the Petition for Allowance of Appeal is GRANTED, and the order of the Commonwealth Court is VACATED. See Commonwealth v. 605 University Drive, 628 Pa. 434, 104 A.3d 411 (2014). This case is REMANDED for consideration of Takeela Burney’s remaining appellate issues.
